## Content Publishing — policy-driven editorial approval
## Agent writes an article, then the ArticleApprovalPolicy requires human approval before publishing.

### Request an article
POST http://localhost:9000/publishing
Content-Type: application/json

{"topic": "The future of renewable energy in urban environments"}

### Check status — look for AWAITING_APPROVAL when the article is ready for review
GET http://localhost:9000/publishing/{{id}}

### Approve publication
POST http://localhost:9000/publishing/{{id}}/approve

### Reject (task fails with the given reason)
POST http://localhost:9000/publishing/{{id}}/reject
Content-Type: application/json

{"reason": "The article needs more concrete examples and data points"}
